'''诺里奇论坛'''（The Forum）是英格兰[[诺福克郡|诺福克郡]][[诺里奇|诺里奇]]的一座建筑，位于[[圣彼得曼科罗夫特教堂|圣彼得曼科罗夫特教堂]]对面。论坛建在1994年被烧毁的原诺里奇图书馆遗址上，由霍普金斯建筑师事务所设计，作为[[东英格兰|东英格兰]]的千年项目，于2001年10月完工，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theforumnorwich.co.uk/media/site-downloads/Architecture__Construction_of_The_Forum.pdf |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2011-04-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110724013335/http://www.theforumnorwich.co.uk/media/site-downloads/Architecture__Construction_of_The_Forum.pdf |archivedate=2011-07-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 论坛是[[诺里奇12|诺里奇12]]系列的一部分，这个系列包括诺里奇的著名建筑，跨越诺曼时代、中世纪、乔治时代、维多利亚时代和现代，每年有250多万人参观。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/onthisday/hi/dates/stories/august/1/newsid_2526000/2526839.stm |title=BBC ON THIS DAY | 1 | 1994: Library fire wipes out historic records |publisher=BBC News |date=1976-08-01 |accessdate=2012-12-20 |archive-date=2020-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920203739/http://news.bbc.co.uk/onthisday/hi/dates/stories/august/1/newsid_2526000/2526839.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theforumnorwich.co.uk/ |title=The Forum, in Norwich - Free Events, Exhibitions, Family Entertainment, Millennium Library, Restaurants, Shops |publisher=Theforumnorwich.co.uk |date= |accessdate=2012-12-20 |archive-date=2021-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423005341/https://theforumnorwich.co.uk/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

